node.text: My sister @chrissperiod had the pleasure of shadowing me for a day 😜Peep the full version on her YouTube

Happy Monday! A little BTS from last week before this epic shot. I love working with my team. They are really amazing. I went to hot yoga this morning & just took my vitamins for the day. I'm off to a great start. Let's get it! I'm taking the next two weeks to workout every single day so send me some good vibes. Im already one week down 💪🏾

node.text: Happy Tuesday! Let's get it. I've been working nonstop, back to eating no meat (I cheated for a while), and trying to enjoy everyday on this floating rock. Hopefully you will see this before tomorrow if the algorithm doesn't try to play me 😎
